13:20.175 --> 13:21.745
but you know what i mean.

13:21.780 --> 13:23.980
It's gonna be great. I promise.

13:24.850 --> 13:25.930
I know.

13:25.940 --> 13:27.360
I just wish we were driving
into the city

13:27.395 --> 13:28.647
instead of taking the train.

13:28.682 --> 13:29.865
I miss being in control.

13:29.900 --> 13:31.270
Yeah, but this way,
we don't have to worry

13:31.305 --> 13:32.930
about parking overnight.

13:33.040 --> 13:34.630
And we can hold hands.

13:36.660 --> 13:38.220
Now i'm glad we didn't drive.

13:41.300 --> 13:42.600
And there it was-

13:42.930 --> 13:44.730
The moment i was looking for,

13:44.980 --> 13:46.780
to tell him how i felt.

13:47.430 --> 13:48.720
Sebastian...

13:51.190 --> 13:52.400
Tickets, please.

13:53.790 --> 13:56.830
And just like that, my moment was gone.

14:00.830 --> 14:02.050
What'd you wanna tell me?

14:02.100 --> 14:03.770
Uh, it can wait.

14:04.980 --> 14:07.480
My perfect moment wasn't going to be here,

14:07.760 --> 14:09.035
but i wasn't worried.

14:09.070 --> 14:10.660
It was going to be a long night.

14:10.695 --> 14:12.080
I'd get other chances...

14:13.720 --> 14:14.900
I hoped.

14:29.820 --> 14:31.450
This place is awesome.

14:31.500 --> 14:33.645
Yawn. It used to be.

14:33.680 --> 14:35.800
Now the only place
that is anyplace in here

14:35.835 --> 14:36.625
